# SecureScan Pro - Environment Variables Template
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file and rename it to ".env", then fill in your actual values.
# The real ".env" file is git-ignored and should NEVER be committed to Git.
#
# How to get your FREE Gemini API key (30 seconds):
#   1. Go to: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#   2. Click [Get API key] --> [Create API key]
#   3. Copy the key (starts with "AIza...")
#   4. Paste it below (replace YOUR_API_KEY_HERE)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
